How to pick a team on My11Circle

Open My11Circle and choose a sport, such as Cricket, Football, Basketball, Baseball, or Kabaddi, from the app’s top bar. Take part in an upcoming match of the sport of your choice.

For that match, pick a squad of your choice. After the squad has been formed, you must select a contest to enter based on the entry price and reward pool.

Each player earns points based on their performance as the game proceeds. The team with the most points at the end of the game wins on My11Circle. Make your squad on My11Circle fantasy cricket app now to get the most out of the Indian T20 League 2022!
